1. *Neophodno* je da se uloži napor u naš rad. (It is necessary to put effort into our work.)

2. Ona je uvidela da je *neophodno* da se promeni. (She realized that it was necessary to change.)

3. *Neophodno* je da učinimo sve što je potrebno da bismo postigli ciljeve. (It is necessary to do all that is necessary to achieve our goals.)

4. Ovde su *neophodne* promene. (Changes are necessary here.)

5. Preporučuje se da se *neophodne* mere preduzmu što pre. (It is recommended to take the necessary measures as soon as possible.)